internal: How can I help you today?
Hello! I am here to assist you. How may I be of service today?

The document is a sample purchase recommendation report. It provides insights into the sales of a particular product or service. The report includes data on the safe price, sales rank trend, internal sales rate, profit/unit, and a recommendation on whether to order more units. I recommend you to order 200 units, as the sales rank trend is improving and the profit/unit is $4.50.

The internal Sales rate of science basics is 50 units/month.
